{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1625306506.6192813", "card_id": "Q_469219832", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2560}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "庆祝中国共产党成立 100 周年大会 7 月 1 日上午在北京天安门广场隆重举行，哪一幕让你印象深刻？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "庆祝中国共产党成立 100 周年大会今日上午 8 时在北京天安门广场隆重举行。中共中央总书记、国家主席、中央军委主席习近平将发表重要讲话。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b2e1c3a0e0e532348901a7e09c208ec5_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3756 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469219832"}}, "attached_info": "ClYIp/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2NTUwNjMzIIn684YGMIEBOKlSQAByCTQ2OTIxOTgzMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1625306506.6200137", "card_id": "Q_469600953", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1158}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待武汉大学邓红兵教授为生化环材专业正名「没有差的专业，只有差的人」?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "高校招生季，志愿填报已经接近尾声，针对社会上形形色色的志愿填报「避坑建议」，武汉大学邓红兵教授公开发文呼吁「高等教育不是教我们谋生，而是教我们创造生活。」「我们的家长们，不要给孩子们挣钱的压力，读书绝不是以发财为目的的」 澎湃新闻记者注意到，7 月 2 日上午，武汉大学官方微博转发了邓红兵教授的这封《致广大考生和家长的一封信》，并点评：「家国情怀、个人兴趣、诚实善良、愈挫愈勇的心态…想必更为重要。因为在热爱与责任面前，所有选择都不应被辜负。」 「天坑」专业被嫌弃，武大教授急坏了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1cdd58ff8ed490908d32faafbe6a557a_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2406 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469600953"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2NjM1NDY0IJCM/IYGMHM4iBhAAXIJNDY5NjAwOTUzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1625306506.620588", "card_id": "Q_467430277", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 164}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "谍战剧的巅峰是《潜伏》吗？为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f63dbce68d2b1dd58338c982370a867f_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "544 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/467430277"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2MTUzMDIzIJ/h1YYGMAs49gRAAnIJNDY3NDMwMjc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1625306506.620942", "card_id": "Q_469220759", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 435}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全国 710 多万名党员获「光荣在党 50 年纪念章」，你身边有获得奖章的人吗？他们身上又有哪些故事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "连日来，全国多个地方和单位陆续举行庄重简朴的仪式，向健在的截至 2021 年 7 月 1 日党龄达到 50 周年、一贯表现良好的老党员颁发「光荣在党 50 年」纪念章。据了解，全国 710 多万名党员获光荣在党 50 年纪念章。跨越半个世纪的光荣，都浓缩在沉甸甸的纪念章里。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-0f3997b909f1b459503c1dd60da622e5_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "455 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469220759"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIp/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2NTUwODQyIO6B9IYGMAE4oQdAA3IJNDY5MjIwNzU5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1625306506.6214314", "card_id": "Q_469242892", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 163}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待小米 MIUI 推出「隐身模式」新功能？会给你的手机使用带来哪些新体验？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，金凡公布了 MIUI 开发版第 502 周更新预告，除了修复一大堆已知问题，还新增了一项名为隐身模式的功能。 据介绍，隐私模式开启之后，所有应用都将无法使用定位、相机、录音三项权限，更好保护用户隐私。 目前该功能已经进入开发版，如果手持开发版 MIUI 的机型，可在设置开启。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6a7fc448fb9cdeee4fde341871a7fd8c_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "368 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469242892"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2NTU1NzU1IOLL9IYGMCY4rwVABHIJNDY5MjQyODkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "