生凹陷。（海外网）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a8d04425ec66591173aba7ad16c23562_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "311 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/469544314"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2NjIyODkwIKWP+4YGMA44uwJAB3IJNDY5NTQ0MzE0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1625306506.623435", "card_id": "Q_468524945", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 64}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些曾经是平民食品现在却变得奢侈化的食物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "镜像问题：有哪些曾经是奢侈食品现在却变得平民化的食物？ - 知乎 "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-2359cb36bbaadbe6a6c442b6c16c3a60_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "286 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/468524945"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDY2Mzk2NDQ4IM+g5oYGMAI4+QFACHIJNDY4NTI0OTQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1625306506.623847", "card_id": "Q_275348817", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "医院的电梯为什么会有专人操作？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一个看起来没什么技术含量的岗位为什么依然存在，主要作用是什么呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-d4b40988e4d96f16ccfd45d19ae04dbe_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "267 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/275348817"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip/Hx9oS1ybYFEAMaCDIzNDY0MzEzILy3mdcFMAM4zAFACXIJMjc1MzQ4ODE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1625306506.6241643", "card_id": "Q_437783371", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 351}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么饭店里的鸡汤很清，而且还特别的好喝？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "因为喜欢喝汤，所以想学怎么做鸡汤，也百度过，可是做出来的汤的味道跟饭店里的鸡